Class ConstVector2d

    • com.company.Vector2d.ConstVector2d

    Vector2d

    public class ConstVector2d
extends java.lang.Object
    Base const class for Vector2d. Encompasses all const-like operations (observers, copying, equality, string conversion) of Vector2d object.
